### Get all persons
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons

### Get info page
GET http://localhost:3001/info

### Get a single person by id (replace <id> with a real id from the GET all response)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons/<id>

### Get a single person with a malformed id (should return 400 malformed id)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons/notavalidid

### Get a single person with a well-formed but nonexistent id (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/persons/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

### Create a new person
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bruce Wayne",
  "number": "040-123-4567"
}

### Create a person with missing number (should return 400 content missing)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No Number Person"
}

### Update an existing person's number (replace <id> with a real id)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/persons/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bruce Wayne",
  "number": "555-111-2323"
}

### Delete a person (replace <id> with a real id)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/persons/<id>
